title: Paul Rabil vs. Awadd Shootout
text:
Paul Rabil vs. Awadd Shootout March 23, 2017 9:34 AM By Chris Lingebach Filed Under: AWadd , Paul Rabil 
WASHINGTON — Major League Lacrosse star Paul Rabil swung by 106.7 The Fan for a special mission Thursday. 
With video producer Adam ‘Awadd’ Epstein all padded up, Rabil fired at will, unleashing an arsenal of lacrosse balls onto his human target. 
But first… target practice!
